# 從頭再嚟

(pos:名詞)
<explanation>
yue: 從頭再嚟 嘅意思（量詞：個）
eng:to start over again

<eg>
yue: 我係從頭再嚟，因為我唔好再錯過機會。 (sai3 man1 zai2.)
eng: I am starting over again because I can't miss the opportunity.

<explanation>
yue: 從頭再嚟 係從頭開始，唔好再重複做過嘅事。 (sai3 man1 zai2.)
eng: Starting over again is not repeating what has been done before.

<eg>
yue: 你從頭再嚟，我係從頭再嚟。 (sai3 man1 zai2.)
eng: You are starting over, I am starting over. [end of text]


